  "original_title": "Dialog partners OnMobile to launch mobile cloud gaming platform ONMO",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Dialog partners OnMobile to launch mobile cloud gaming platform ONMO",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Dialog Axiata PLC, Sri Lanka\u2019s premier connectivity provider, partnered OnMobile, the global leader in mobile entertainment, to launch ONMO (www.onmo.dgl.lk) to provide Dialog mobile customers a unique, immersive and interactive gaming experience.",
        "ONMO, a mobile gaming platform that blends cloud streaming, social Esports and Artificial Intelligence (AI), offers Dialog mobile users access to more than 60 exciting mobile games spanning genres such as action, arcade, racing, adventure, puzzles, and more with new games added every week. Users can enjoy ONMO and all of its wide range of games for Rs. 399 + taxes per month. ONMO\u2019s challenge creation Vision AI engine brings casual Esports to everyone on a social platform with no friction and with no prior download necessary. The platform also offers a social play aspect, with short, curated game moments and virtual rewards, along with many more exciting features.",
        "Speaking on the launch of the platform, Dialog Axiata PLC Group Chief Innovation Officer and Chief Architect Anthony Rodrigo stated, \u201cDialog is excited to be the first to launch a commercial cloud gaming platform in Sri Lanka in collaboration with our partner, OnMobile. This cloud gaming platform has been optimised for smartphones and to seamlessly run on Dialog\u2019s 4G mobile and Home Broadband networks. We are also excited to witness the full potential that 5G will unlock for Cloud Gaming in future for all Sri Lankans.\u201d",
        "ONMO CEO Krish Seshadri said, \u201cWe believe ONMO will emerge as a go-to-destination for cloud gaming in the region. We are excited to partner with Dialog to launch the first cloud gaming platform in Sri Lanka. The social play aspect, short, curated game moments and virtual rewards will make ONMO a fun and engaging experience for Dialog consumers.\u201d"
      ],
